<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Old_Persian_language&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7" title="Edit section: Grammar">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="Grammar">Grammar</span></h2>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Old_Persian_language&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8" title="Edit section: Nouns">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="Nouns">Nouns</span></h3>
<p>Old Persian stems:</p>
<ul>
<li>a-stems (-a, -am, -ā)</li>
<li>i-stems (-iš, iy)</li>
<li>u- (and au-) stems (-uš, -uv)</li>
<li>consonantal stems (n, r, h)</li>
</ul>
