<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Old_Persian_language&amp;action=edit&amp;section=11" title="Edit section: See also">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="See_also">See also</span></h2>
<div class="noprint tright portal" style="border:solid #aaa 1px;margin:0.5em 0 0.5em 0.5em;">
